## How to run locally & offline (quick)
1. Create app (if not already):
```bash
npx create-react-app payal-surprise
cd payal-surprise
```
2. Replace `src/App.js` and `src/App.css` with the files above. Remove default extra code if necessary.
3. Test:
```bash
npm start
# open http://localhost:3000
```
4. Build for offline:
```bash
npm run build
# then serve the build folder or copy it to a laptop and open build/index.html
# optional: npx serve build
```

